WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.000
[Unknown]: I. V. M.

00:00:04.280 --> 00:00:06.280
[Amit Varma]: I had a strange dream the other day.

00:00:06.600 --> 00:00:11.120
[Amit Varma]: I dreamed I was a fly on the wall at a swayamvar in 1973.

00:00:11.320 --> 00:00:14.440
[Amit Varma]: Now a swayamvar is a practice in which a bunch of men,

00:00:14.640 --> 00:00:16.280
[Amit Varma]: all dressed up and objectified,

00:00:16.560 --> 00:00:19.120
[Amit Varma]: line up in a hall while a woman walks among them

00:00:19.280 --> 00:00:20.680
[Amit Varma]: with a garland in her hand.

00:00:21.000 --> 00:00:23.760
[Amit Varma]: She picks one of these men as her marital partner

00:00:23.960 --> 00:00:25.320
[Amit Varma]: and puts a garland around him.

00:00:25.720 --> 00:00:27.880
[Amit Varma]: Now the swayamvar is an ancient tradition,

00:00:27.880 --> 00:00:29.800
[Amit Varma]: but this was a modern swayamvar.

00:00:30.040 --> 00:00:32.640
[Amit Varma]: The girl was allowed to ask questions.

00:00:33.080 --> 00:00:34.960
[Amit Varma]: So the girl was walking up to each man

00:00:35.160 --> 00:00:36.800
[Amit Varma]: and asking him just one question.

00:00:37.120 --> 00:00:38.640
[Amit Varma]: What did he do for a living?

00:00:39.040 --> 00:00:41.520
[Amit Varma]: The first contender was a thin boy

00:00:41.720 --> 00:00:43.800
[Amit Varma]: with thick glasses wearing a dhoti kurta.

00:00:44.000 --> 00:00:45.960
[Amit Varma]: What do you do for a living, she asked him.

00:00:46.200 --> 00:00:49.680
[Amit Varma]: He said, I am doing my PhD in aeronautics.

00:00:50.600 --> 00:00:52.680
[Amit Varma]: She shrugged and went to the next guy.

00:00:53.200 --> 00:00:56.840
[Amit Varma]: The next chap, his hair slicked back in a center parting,

00:00:56.840 --> 00:01:00.360
[Amit Varma]: wearing a beige churidar kurta with the jacket of a safari suit,

00:01:00.680 --> 00:01:03.160
[Amit Varma]: said, I am an IAS officer.

00:01:03.800 --> 00:01:06.160
[Amit Varma]: The garland twitched in her fingers,

00:01:06.440 --> 00:01:07.840
[Amit Varma]: but she walked away.

00:01:08.280 --> 00:01:12.400
[Amit Varma]: The next person in line was a tall, geeky, tambram in a vesti.

00:01:12.720 --> 00:01:14.280
[Amit Varma]: She asked him the same question.

00:01:14.520 --> 00:01:16.920
[Amit Varma]: He replied, I am a software engineer.

00:01:17.120 --> 00:01:20.040
[Amit Varma]: See, this is 1973 and you may wonder what that is,

00:01:20.240 --> 00:01:23.760
[Amit Varma]: but wait 30 years and I'll be the hottest thing around.

00:01:23.760 --> 00:01:26.560
[Amit Varma]: She very rudely showed him a thanga and walked on.

00:01:27.080 --> 00:01:32.240
[Amit Varma]: Finally, she came to a young man wearing a flowery t-shirt and bell-bottom pants.

00:01:32.560 --> 00:01:36.440
[Amit Varma]: He had the face of Prem Chopra and the swagger of Amitabh Bachchan.

00:01:36.720 --> 00:01:39.840
[Amit Varma]: She asked him the same question and he replied,

00:01:40.760 --> 00:01:43.040
[Amit Varma]: I do import-export.

00:01:43.560 --> 00:01:44.960
[Amit Varma]: And well, the story ends here.

00:01:45.160 --> 00:01:46.560
[Amit Varma]: They lived happily ever after.

